<div id="wechat">
<p>新年第一天，几位朋友问我罗胖2022年跨年演讲里面提及的那个《左手六分满的玻璃杯》的实验具体是怎么回事。</p>
<section><iframe allowfullscreen="" class="video_iframe rich_pages" data-cover="http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FficMBQYNIo0cLL5tPCFWCnRtqAkqCliajus89zk6vulqL97ZTH6neMeuD1Z24fdyh4Rq54DXMrE3qWospvibaDLag%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg" data-mpvid="wxv_2204937563042349057" data-ratio="2.064516129032258" data-src="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_2204937563042349057" data-vidtype="2" data-w="1280" frameborder="0"></iframe></section>
<section></section>
<p>我把很久以前的那篇文章转发一下。谢谢罗胖的提及。</p>
<p><a data-itemshowtype="0" data-linktype="2" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzI0Mjg0MA==&amp;mid=2652373084&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1d29e95566d1a3c81b1a39499965c853&amp;chksm=bd3052eb8a47dbfd23ce847d8657d3e1ae18b747ec7562504f7654ec350d68f4d3ef83d2d733&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" imgdata="null" imgurl="" linktype="text" tab="innerlink" target="_blank" textvalue="喂养青龙的、左手边六分满的玻璃杯" rel="noopener"><span style="font-size: 20px;">喂养青龙的、左手边六分满的玻璃杯</span></a></p>
<h1 style='margin-bottom: 14px;outline: 0px;font-size: 22px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;'></h1>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-weight: 700;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">缘起</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">有本关于风水的书提及</span></p>
<section style="margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 48px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-weight: 700;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">在办公桌的左手位，放一玻璃杯，一直保持6分水，大吉！</span></span></section>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">解释是这样的：</span></p>
<section style="margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 48px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;border: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: 700;vertical-align: baseline;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">左青龙，右白虎</span>。</span></section>
<section style="margin-right: 48px;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 48px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">青龙喜水，左手位放一杯水，青龙随时有水喝，主人的生活就会比较调和。</span></section>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">我心想：“见过不靠谱的，没见过这么不靠谱的。” 然后把书扔了了事。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-weight: 700;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">实验</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">不久前，我整理完桌面，在琢磨玻璃杯子应该放在哪里的时候，想起这句话，决定不妨试一下，把杯子放在左手边，并且盛了六分满的水。同时暗笑自己迂腐，居然这等玄学也信。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">过了两天，我就意识到，自己喝水的次数明显增加。每当我有意识的注意到杯子的时候，杯子却总是空的。什么时候喝的？不记得了。于是赶紧盛好水，心想，“青龙要紧”，然后再忙自己的事情，当再看杯子的时候，水不知不觉的已经喝到肚子里去了，于是又加到六分。。。一天下来，我居然平均能喝八到十杯水。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">我之后试了一下，放在右手边，大约 4 杯左右；放在身后，经常一天不喝水。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-weight: 700;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">道理</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">万事皆有其理，不过不是原来他们说的那个道理。我就努力的想这其中的道理。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么一定要放在左手边呢？</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">我猜测，因为绝大多数的人用右手写字，做事情，用鼠标。水杯放在左手边让我们可以在不停下手里的事情的情况下，甚至在不中断思路的情况下喝水。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么是玻璃杯呢？</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">我猜测，这是容易让人看到水，从而提醒人喝水。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">为什么一定要六分满呢？</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">超过六分满的水一定会比剩一个杯底更容易让人产生喝水的冲动。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">以上都是我的臆测，没有经过实验，所以仅仅是猜测。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">不过，科学和经验的差别在于，科学在于不断的假设，论证，推翻或者证明中前行。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">科学和玄学</strong></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">Brian Wansink就是一个这样的科学家。他写了一本有趣的书，</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">Mindless Eating</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">（《无意识的进食》）。他用大量的科学实验证明：我们的行动是多么容易受环境的影响。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">他举了</span>些<span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">有趣的例子：</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果你的勺子比较大，比较容易吃得多；</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果把饼干盒子挪开桌子2米远，就会少吃一半左右的零食；</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果一边吃鸡，一边有人把鸡骨头拿掉，就比不这么做容易吃更多；</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果碗里的汤一直保持在一半以上，人容易吃得更多；</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果吃饭的人比较多，人也容易吃得更多。</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">其实这个说法和风水的说法异曲同工，不过一个是经过经验，一个是经过实验，得到类似的道理。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-weight: 700;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">风水 = 方便 + 时间</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以我开始相信某些风水的说法，虽然它经常被包装，被神秘化，被曲解，但有其事八成是有其理的。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">风水研究的事情，从来不是<span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;border: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: 700;vertical-align: baseline;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">可为</span>还是<span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;border: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: 700;vertical-align: baseline;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">不可为</span>的区别，都是<span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;border: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: 700;vertical-align: baseline;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">方便</span>和<span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;border: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-weight: 700;vertical-align: baseline;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">不方便</span>的区别，就像挪一个屏风，摆弄一下花草，换一个床的位置等等。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">而</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">方便和不方便</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">，导致了每天哪怕是百分之一，千分之一，甚至更少的差别。但是，因为它发生在我们的家里、办公室里，我们每天都被这样的环境潜移默化的影响着。一天，两天，甚至几个月或许都不会有什么看得到的区别，但是一年，两年呢？比如我相信，如果我们天多喝一杯水，一年以后，身体还是应该有些变化的。</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">风水之所以听起来那么玄虚，或许就是因为</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">它产生的变化，是如此之微小</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">，仅仅是一个更加方便一点点的区别；但是我们常常忘了，这一点点的变化，经过足够长时间的积累，就足以产生巨大的改变。</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;text-align: start;border: 0px;font-family: Lato, sans-serif;vertical-align: baseline;caret-color: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(43, 43, 43);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 17px;">能把一个小改动和长时间的积累联系在一起，看出其因果关系，的确需要几百年的经验和智慧的积累。</span><span style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>
</div>
